freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Enlarged supraclavicular lymph node on the injection side
Enlarged supraclavicular lymph node on the injection side. Moderately painful to palpation. Mildly painful with AROM of neck and right arm.
Size of previously reported supra clavicular lymph node is going down. Not painful.
There is mild soreness around the injection site like there is with the flu shot
